<h2>Pairing Suggestions</h2>

<p>Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel is delicious on its own, but it can also be paired with other foods and beverages to create a more elaborate tasting experience. Here are a few suggestions:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Wine:</strong> Pair with a full-bodied red wine like Cabernet Sauvignon or a sweet dessert wine like Port.</li>
    <li><strong>Coffee:</strong> Enjoy with a cup of freshly brewed coffee or espresso for a delightful contrast of flavors.</li>
    <li><strong>Cheese:</strong> Pair with a sharp cheddar or creamy brie for a sophisticated dessert platter.</li>
    <li><strong>Fruit:</strong> Serve with fresh berries or sliced apples for a refreshing and healthy twist.</li>
</ul>

<h2>FAQs</h2>

<div class="faq">
    <h3>Is Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel really gluten-free?</h3>
    <p>Yes, Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel is gluten-free. The brand takes extra precautions to ensure that their products are free from gluten-containing ingredients and cross-contamination.</p>

    <h3>How many calories are in one square of Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel?</h3>
    <p>One square of Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel contains approximately 70 calories.</p>

    <h3>Can I eat Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel if I have a nut allergy?</h3>
    <p>While Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel does not contain nuts, it is produced in a facility that also processes nuts. If you have a severe nut allergy, it's best to consult with your doctor before consuming this product.</p>

    <h3>Where can I buy Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel?</h3>
    <p>Ghirardelli Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel is widely available at grocery stores, specialty food stores, and online retailers. You can also purchase it directly from the Ghirardelli website.</p>
